            <title>[MNG-1011] &lt;defaultGoal&gt; doesn&apos;t work</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MNG-1011</link>
                <project id="12316922" key="MNG">Maven (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;added the following to pom.xml:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  &amp;lt;build&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;defaultGoal&amp;gt;install&amp;lt;/defaultGoal&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;/build&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On command line, type: m2&lt;/p&gt;

