You must specify at least one goal. Try &apos;install&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;usage: maven &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;options&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; [goal [goal2 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;goal3&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; ...]]&lt;/p&gt;

